# bitReversalPermutation

- _bitReversalPermutation(k)_

Answer the _bit-reversal permutation_ for a sequence of size _2 ^ k_.

```
>>> 0:4.collect(bitReversalPermutation:/1)
[
	1;
	1 2;
	1 3 2 4;
	1 5 3 7 2 6 4 8;
	1 9 5 13 3 11 7 15 2 10 6 14 4 12 8 16
]
```

